@startuml sequence_borrow_highlevel
title Borrow Book - High-Level Sequence (Stakeholders)

actor Member
actor Librarian
participant "Library System" as LMS
participant "Email Service" as Email

Member -> Librarian : Ask to borrow a book
Librarian -> LMS : Submit borrow request (memberId, bookId)
LMS -> LMS : Authenticate staff and validate member
LMS -> LMS : Check book availability

alt Validation failed or book unavailable
  LMS --> Librarian : Borrow denied with reason
  Librarian --> Member : Explain issue and next step
else Borrow approved
  LMS -> LMS : Create loan and update book status
  LMS --> Librarian : Borrow confirmed (due date)
  Librarian --> Member : Hand over book and due date
  LMS -> Email : Send loan confirmation
  Email --> Member : Confirmation email
end

@enduml
